pem: Easy PEM file parsing
==========================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pem.svg
   :target: https://pypi.org/project/pem/
   :alt: PyPI

.. image:: https://readthedocs.org/projects/pem/badge/?version=stable
